org.opentcs.access.rmi

Interface KernelProxy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventSource<TCSEvent>, Kernel, RemoteKernelConnection

    public interface KernelProxy
extends Kernel, RemoteKernelConnection
    A proxy for a Kernel instance that hides the details of communication with a remote kernel, so a client can call methods of the proxy as if it was a reference to a kernel instance within the same JVM. Allows to login/logout cleanly and repeatedly.
    See Also:
    KernelProxyBuilder
